<SYNC Start=14400><P Class=ENCC>Roger, it's good to see you.
<SYNC Start=16038><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=16120><P Class=ENCC>I'd like to talk to you about this meeting.<br>I don't trust the ambassador.
<SYNC Start=20193><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=20280><P Class=ENCC>It's possible that his country's<br>supporting Second Wave.
<SYNC Start=23511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=23600><P Class=ENCC>We want to prevent this incident.
<SYNC Start=26512><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=26600><P Class=ENCC>We need access to your files.
<SYNC Start=28477><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=28560><P Class=ENCC>I want you to monitor<br>how they use our intel.
<SYNC Start=31028><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=31760><P Class=ENCC>It's the ambassador's chopper.<br>It crashed just after takeoff.
<SYNC Start=35309><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=36400><P Class=ENCC>- There's a man who needs to talk to you.<br>- Who is he?
<SYNC Start=39517><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=39600><P Class=ENCC>He's from the Counter Terrorism Agency?
<SYNC Start=42114><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=42200><P Class=ENCC>I told you, I do not know a Syed Ali.
<SYNC Start=44111><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=44200><P Class=ENCC>Then how do you explain that his name<br>is in your personal computer files?
<SYNC Start=48352><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=48800><P Class=ENCC>There's a nuclear bomb in Los Angeles.<br>Do what I tell you. Go now.
<SYNC Start=53430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=53520><P Class=ENCC>Miguel, get over here.
<SYNC Start=54919><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=55000><P Class=ENCC>There's a nuclear bomb in the city.
<SYNC Start=56638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=56720><P Class=ENCC>- Let's get outta here.<br>- Not without Megan.
<SYNC Start=59518><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=59960><P Class=ENCC>George, I got to Wald. I found out<br>who commissioned him to take out CTU.
<SYNC Start=63794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=63880><P Class=ENCC>- Who was it?<br>- It was Nina Myers.
<SYNC Start=65871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=65960><P Class=ENCC>Nina?
<SYNC Start=66870><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=66960><P Class=ENCC>Nina killed your wife.<br>I don't want you near her.
<SYNC Start=69315><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=69400><P Class=ENCC>(Palmer) I have to grant her<br>a shadow asylum.
<SYNC Start=71960><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=72040><P Class=ENCC>That sounds like a pardon, sir.
<SYNC Start=73871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=73960><P Class=ENCC>She has information<br>that could help us find this bomb.
<SYNC Start=77032><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=77120><P Class=ENCC>- What is it?<br>- They're gonna let her go.
<SYNC Start=79714><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=80160><P Class=ENCC>I know you were exposed to high levels<br>of radioactive materials this morning.
<SYNC Start=84358><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=84440><P Class=ENCC>I wanna know what your plans are for Nina.<br>I want the case. I know how she thinks.
<SYNC Start=88558><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=88640><P Class=ENCC>If you don't do this, I'll tell District<br>about your condition. They'll replace you.
<SYNC Start=92599><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=137920><P Class=ENCC>Palmerjust signed the pardon. So, as soon<br>as it gets here, we'll start the interrogation.
<SYNC Start=143870><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=158360><P Class=ENCC>- Nina's file.<br>- I don't need it.
<SYNC Start=161352><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=178200><P Class=ENCC>The president's here.
<SYNC Start=179519><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=194360><P Class=ENCC>Mr President...
<SYNC Start=196032><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=196120><P Class=ENCC>Mr President, can you give us any<br>details about the helicopter crash?
<SYNC Start=200955><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=201040><P Class=ENCC>- Who was on the aircraft? Any survivors?<br>- Is it related to the bombing in LA?
<SYNC Start=207354><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=207440><P Class=ENCC>We can't disclose information<br>about the crash
<SYNC Start=209874><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=209960><P Class=ENCC>until the families of the victims<br>have been notified.
<SYNC Start=212918><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=213000><P Class=ENCC>But I promise you, there will be<br>a careful and thorough investigation.
<SYNC Start=217073><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=217160><P Class=ENCC>- Mr President...<br>- Let's go.
<SYNC Start=219151><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=219240><P Class=ENCC>We will be putting out a formal statement<br>as soon as we get those issues resolved,
<SYNC Start=224030><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=224120><P Class=ENCC>and I ask everyone to refrain<br>from speculation until that time.
<SYNC Start=228272><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=228360><P Class=ENCC>No one besides Jenny releases<br>a statement on the crash.
<SYNC Start=231397><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=231480><P Class=ENCC>No names, no speculation.<br>And keep the lid on tight.
<SYNC Start=234438><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=234520><P Class=ENCC>Absolutely, sir.
<SYNC Start=236511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=250000><P Class=ENCC>Hello, David.
<SYNC Start=252150><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=252240><P Class=ENCC>How did you get in here<br>without my authorisation?
<SYNC Start=255152><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=255240><P Class=ENCC>We were married for many years. Many<br>people respect that, even if you don't.
<SYNC Start=260917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=261000><P Class=ENCC>I need to talk to you.
<SYNC Start=262718><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=262800><P Class=ENCC>We have nothing more to talk about.<br>You're not my wife any more.
<SYNC Start=267032><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=267120><P Class=ENCC>- It's not about us.<br>- Then what?
<SYNC Start=269714><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=273720><P Class=ENCC>Not here. I need to be alone with you.
<SYNC Start=277508><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=277600><P Class=ENCC>You know what?
<SYNC Start=279318><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=279400><P Class=ENCC>Even if I were interested in what<br>you had to say, today is impossible.
<SYNC Start=284110><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=284200><P Class=ENCC>You shouldn't have come here.
<SYNC Start=286760><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=286840><P Class=ENCC>- It's about your administration.<br>- What about it?
<SYNC Start=289912><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=290000><P Class=ENCC>- Just give me five minutes.<br>- I don't have time now.
<SYNC Start=292958><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=293040><P Class=ENCC>Did you order an evacuation of<br>military personnel out of Los Angeles?
<SYNC Start=298956><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=315920><P Class=ENCC>Who told you that?
<SYNC Start=317911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=319640><P Class=ENCC>Five minutes, David.
<SYNC Start=321870><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=324280><P Class=ENCC>Wait here.
<SYNC Start=326430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=326520><P Class=ENCC>I'll call you.
<SYNC Start=328909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=335480><P Class=ENCC>Do we know about the military<br>moving personnel out of LA?
<SYNC Start=338677><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=338760><P Class=ENCC>No. Sir, you specifically requested<br>there be no evacuation.
<SYNC Start=343390><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=343480><P Class=ENCC>- Check into it.<br>- I certainly will.
<SYNC Start=346040><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=346800><P Class=ENCC>You're doing business<br>with a known terrorist,
<SYNC Start=350076><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=350160><P Class=ENCC>and you sit there with a straight face<br>and tell me you don't know what's going on?
<SYNC Start=356156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=359280><P Class=ENCC>I grew up in London. I'm marrying<br>an American girl, a Protestant.
<SYNC Start=364559><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=366440><P Class=ENCC>So, if you're going to racially profile me,
<SYNC Start=370479><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=371840><P Class=ENCC>you should at least get it right.
<SYNC Start=374229><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=374320><P Class=ENCC>Our main targets are European Muslims
<SYNC Start=377710><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=377800><P Class=ENCC>with western educations, passports,
<SYNC Start=380872><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=380960><P Class=ENCC>and the potential<br>to blend into western society.
<SYNC Start=385272><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=386800><P Class=ENCC>So tell me, Reza,<br>how's my racial profiling going now?
<SYNC Start=390793><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=392360><P Class=ENCC>I want a lawyer.
<SYNC Start=394510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=395440><P Class=ENCC>No.
<SYNC Start=396759><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=399400><P Class=ENCC>- Did they find the black box yet?<br>- Not yet, Mr President.
<SYNC Start=403473><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=403560><P Class=ENCC>How could something like this happen?
<SYNC Start=405710><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=405800><P Class=ENCC>I don't know. I've opened a multi-agency<br>investigation. NTSB is on the way.
<SYNC Start=411511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=411600><P Class=ENCC>Lynne, schedule a call<br>with the prime minister.
<SYNC Start=414478><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=414560><P Class=ENCC>- Yes, sir.<br>- I wanna talk to him before rumours start.
<SYNC Start=418348><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=418440><P Class=ENCC>But I'm afraid they may not be far from<br>the truth. This was not an accident.
<SYNC Start=423468><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=423560><P Class=ENCC>I'm thinking along<br>the same lines, Mr President.
<SYNC Start=426996><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=427080><P Class=ENCC>The prime minister may not have been happy<br>about the ambassador's cooperation with us.
<SYNC Start=432552><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=432640><P Class=ENCC>There's another possibility, Roger.
<SYNC Start=435598><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=435680><P Class=ENCC>I'm not following you, sir.
<SYNC Start=438513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=438960><P Class=ENCC>- That we did it.<br>- Correct.
<SYNC Start=441838><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=443040><P Class=ENCC>That hardly seems likely.
<SYNC Start=444632><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=444720><P Class=ENCC>The ambassador took classified<br>information back to his government.
<SYNC Start=448429><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=448520><P Class=ENCC>- You both thought it was questionable.<br>- And if we were talking about it here,
<SYNC Start=452718><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=452800><P Class=ENCC>you can bet there are others back<br>in DC who feel even more strongly.
<SYNC Start=457191><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=457280><P Class=ENCC>Set up an independent investigator.<br>Let's find out exactly who was in the loop.
<SYNC Start=461876><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=461960><P Class=ENCC>Yes, sir.
<SYNC Start=463518><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=472480><P Class=ENCC>OK, this is it. Here we go.
<SYNC Start=475040><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=476840><P Class=ENCC>I'll show her this, I'll let her start talking.
<SYNC Start=479559><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=479640><P Class=ENCC>Then I'll get you the stuff<br>she doesn't want us to know.
<SYNC Start=483110><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=483200><P Class=ENCC>The last time I let you interrogate<br>somebody, you shot him through the heart.
<SYNC Start=487478><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=487560><P Class=ENCC>I'm letting you do this,<br>but I hope I'm not making a mistake.
<SYNC Start=490711><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=490800><P Class=ENCC>No mistake, George.
<SYNC Start=493155><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=494120><P Class=ENCC>All right. Good luck.
<SYNC Start=496111><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=550600><P Class=ENCC>Let's keep this simple.
<SYNC Start=552238><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=552320><P Class=ENCC>If you wanna stop the bomb,<br>I need to be on a plane to Visalia now.
<SYNC Start=557474><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=557560><P Class=ENCC>Did you pick Visalia for a reason, or would<br>anywhere outside the blast zone work?
<SYNC Start=562031><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=562120><P Class=ENCC>- My contact is in Visalia.<br>- Who is it?
<SYNC Start=565476><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=565560><P Class=ENCC>The only person who can<br>tell us where the bomb is.
<SYNC Start=569109><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=569200><P Class=ENCC>I'm not gonna tell you who it is<br>till we get there.
<SYNC Start=572397><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=572480><P Class=ENCC>Fine. Then you can sit here<br>and wait for the blast to hit.
<SYNC Start=577759><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=577840><P Class=ENCC>Stop wasting time.<br>I have the president's signature.
<SYNC Start=581469><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=581560><P Class=ENCC>I'm here. He's not.
<SYNC Start=584199><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=584280><P Class=ENCC>And I'm not gonna make a move<br>until I believe you're credible.
<SYNC Start=587875><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=587960><P Class=ENCC>I'll only get the pardon if I stop the bomb.<br>Why wouldn't I do everything I can?
<SYNC Start=592317><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=592400><P Class=ENCC>Because you're worse than a traitor, Nina.
<SYNC Start=595392><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=595480><P Class=ENCC>You don't have a cause.<br>You don't believe in anything.
<SYNC Start=598597><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=598680><P Class=ENCC>But you would sell anyone out<br>to the highest bidder.
<SYNC Start=601752><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=601840><P Class=ENCC>So stop wasting my time! Gimme a name!
<SYNC Start=605958><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=609520><P Class=ENCC>Don't even bother, Jack.
<SYNC Start=611511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=611600><P Class=ENCC>If you lay a hand on me,<br>you'll be taken off the case.
<SYNC Start=615388><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=636200><P Class=ENCC>You're just gonna have to follow my lead.
<SYNC Start=639590><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=649360><P Class=ENCC>Tell me everything I wanna know,
<SYNC Start=651396><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=651480><P Class=ENCC>or I swear to God, I will hurt you<br>before I kill you and no one will stop me.
<SYNC Start=655837><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=655920><P Class=ENCC>- Do you understand?<br>- (Mason) Jack, let her go! Now!
<SYNC Start=658878><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=658960><P Class=ENCC>(gasps)
<SYNC Start=660951><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=676440><P Class=ENCC>- All right, you're done. Get outta here.<br>- Why?
<SYNC Start=679113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=679200><P Class=ENCC>Why? Because you've lost it! That's why.
<SYNC Start=681668><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=681760><P Class=ENCC>Right now she thinks she's<br>won the lottery. She's in control.
<SYNC Start=685548><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=685640><P Class=ENCC>You want her to tell the truth, take that away.
<SYNC Start=688074><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=688160><P Class=ENCC>By killing her? That'll work.
<SYNC Start=690071><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=690160><P Class=ENCC>By giving her someone to answer to,<br>someone to be afraid of.
<SYNC Start=693470><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=693560><P Class=ENCC>She has to believe I'd be willing to put<br>my revenge over finding this bomb.
<SYNC Start=697872><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=697960><P Class=ENCC>- And you're telling me you're not.<br>- George, it had to look like that.
<SYNC Start=701873><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=701960><P Class=ENCC>Look at me. There's no emotion here.
<SYNC Start=705794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=705880><P Class=ENCC>Now look at her.
<SYNC Start=708030><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=709240><P Class=ENCC>- What would your next move be?<br>- You need to let me go back in there,
<SYNC Start=714030><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=714120><P Class=ENCC>show her that I have the power<br>to do anything I want to her.
<SYNC Start=719353><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=725960><P Class=ENCC>- If I let you go back in there, you've got...<br>- All I need is five minutes.
<SYNC Start=731114><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=732440><P Class=ENCC>Just don't let anyone in that room<br>and raise the thermostat ten degrees.
<SYNC Start=738390><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=739200><P Class=ENCC>Are you gonna let me have five minutes?
<SYNC Start=742272><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=744480><P Class=ENCC>Yeah.
<SYNC Start=745708><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=746840><P Class=ENCC>Thank you.
<SYNC Start=748319><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=758600><P Class=ENCC>In the latest update,<br>we have Mr President requesting...
<SYNC Start=763276><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=774360><P Class=ENCC>We need to talk.
<SYNC Start=776510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=778160><P Class=ENCC>I told you to leave.
<SYNC Start=780913><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=781000><P Class=ENCC>Well...
<SYNC Start=783468><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=783560><P Class=ENCC>I'm not leaving.
<SYNC Start=786028><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=786120><P Class=ENCC>I'm your sister,
<SYNC Start=787997><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=788440><P Class=ENCC>and you can stay angry with me,
<SYNC Start=791273><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=791360><P Class=ENCC>but we need to figure out<br>what we're going to do.
<SYNC Start=794796><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=794880><P Class=ENCC>Do about what?
<SYNC Start=797678><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=797760><P Class=ENCC>The wedding.
<SYNC Start=799751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=803760><P Class=ENCC>We may have to cancel.
<SYNC Start=806320><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=808400><P Class=ENCC>That would make you happy, wouldn't it?<br>Isn't that what you wanted all along?
<SYNC Start=813235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=813320><P Class=ENCC>No. Not the marriage, Marie.
<SYNC Start=816278><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=816360><P Class=ENCC>Just the wedding.
<SYNC Start=818430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=819520><P Class=ENCC>We can't do it today.<br>Let me help you take care of it.
<SYNC Start=823672><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=823760><P Class=ENCC>You are always pretending<br>you wanna help me.
<SYNC Start=826433><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=826520><P Class=ENCC>Pretending?
<SYNC Start=828511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=830000><P Class=ENCC>I dropped out of school when Mom died to<br>take care of you, to keep this family together.
<SYNC Start=835836><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=835920><P Class=ENCC>So you'd have an excuse<br>for not having a relationship.
<SYNC Start=838992><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=839080><P Class=ENCC>"Dad needs me. Marie needs me." Now I don't<br>need you any more, you can't handle it!
<SYNC Start=843312><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=843400><P Class=ENCC>- I made sacrifices because...<br>- Then stop! Mom died a long time ago!
<SYNC Start=847393><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=847480><P Class=ENCC>So get your own life and stay outta mine!<br>We are not cancelling this wedding!
<SYNC Start=852235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=856440><P Class=ENCC>She's not in intensive care or<br>the east wing. She's gotta be up here.
<SYNC Start=859989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=860080><P Class=ENCC>How much time do we have to this nuke?
<SYNC Start=863117><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=863200><P Class=ENCC>- I don't know.<br>- What if Megan doesn't wanna come with us?
<SYNC Start=866795><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=866880><P Class=ENCC>I don't know.
<SYNC Start=868871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=870800><P Class=ENCC>That's him.
<SYNC Start=872791><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=879760><P Class=ENCC>Mr Matheson?
<SYNC Start=882149><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=885360><P Class=ENCC>The MRI confirmed that the pressure on<br>the brain was the result of the concussion.
<SYNC Start=890275><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=891120><P Class=ENCC>Meaning?
<SYNC Start=892394><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=892480><P Class=ENCC>That we won't release her until questions<br>about the sources of her injuries are resolved.
<SYNC Start=898032><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=899040><P Class=ENCC>Of course. Listen, I just wanna<br>do what's best for my little girl.
<SYNC Start=903113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=904040><P Class=ENCC>Good. I'll check in on her<br>at the end of my rounds.
<SYNC Start=908033><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=909520><P Class=ENCC>And, Mr Matheson, no cellphones in the<br>hospital. They interfere with the equipment.
<SYNC Start=915197><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=915280><P Class=ENCC>Of course. Sorry.
<SYNC Start=917510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=921200><P Class=ENCC>(dials phone)
<SYNC Start=923191><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=924480><P Class=ENCC>Daddy, are you still mad at me?
<SYNC Start=927517><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=927600><P Class=ENCC>No, sweetie, no. Everything's fine.<br>Daddy's just tired.
<SYNC Start=931878><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=931960><P Class=ENCC>You need to get dressed, OK?
<SYNC Start=934679><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=934760><P Class=ENCC>- Mr Matheson's office.<br>- Chelsea, it's me.
<SYNC Start=937638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=937720><P Class=ENCC>Do something for me. Book me two seats<br>on the next flight to Mexico City.
<SYNC Start=941872><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=941960><P Class=ENCC>- But you have a meeting...<br>- I know. I'm asking you to cancel it.
<SYNC Start=946272><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=946360><P Class=ENCC>- What about your five o'clock?<br>- Cancel everything.
<SYNC Start=950433><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=954880><P Class=ENCC>(door opens)
<SYNC Start=956871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=961120><P Class=ENCC>Who is the man in Visalia?
<SYNC Start=963793><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=968360><P Class=ENCC>Who is the man in Visalia?
<SYNC Start=971079><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=971160><P Class=ENCC>Mamud Faheen.<br>The man in Visalia is Mamud Faheen.
<SYNC Start=974436><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=974520><P Class=ENCC>That's not news! We've got his name!
<SYNC Start=976670><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=976760><P Class=ENCC>But you don't know where he is. I do.
<SYNC Start=979718><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=979800><P Class=ENCC>- What's the history of the relationship?<br>- He introduced me to Wald.
<SYNC Start=984237><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=984320><P Class=ENCC>So Wald could buy the schematics<br>for CTU and blow it up as a diversion?
<SYNC Start=989155><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=989240><P Class=ENCC>I didn't know it was part of a plan<br>to detonate a nuclear device.
<SYNC Start=992676><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=992760><P Class=ENCC>Then why are you so sure<br>Faheen's involved?
<SYNC Start=995274><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=995360><P Class=ENCC>I heard hints that he was involved<br>in something in Los Angeles.
<SYNC Start=998796><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=998880><P Class=ENCC>Something substantial.
<SYNC Start=1001394><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1009320><P Class=ENCC>Where is he in Visalia now?
<SYNC Start=1012312><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1012400><P Class=ENCC>I'm not gonna give you his location<br>until we get there.
<SYNC Start=1016234><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1016320><P Class=ENCC>(click)
<SYNC Start=1018038><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1018120><P Class=ENCC>If you could get to him, you wouldn't need<br>me. My deal would do me no good if I'm dead.
<SYNC Start=1024116><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1039200><P Class=ENCC>Get me Visalia.
<SYNC Start=1041191><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1064880><P Class=ENCC>Sir...
<SYNC Start=1066359><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1067640><P Class=ENCC>Sherry was right. An evacuation of<br>military personnel began about an hour ago,
<SYNC Start=1072714><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1072800><P Class=ENCC>which means it is well under way.
<SYNC Start=1074791><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1074880><P Class=ENCC>- Do we know where this order came from?<br>- Yes, we do, sir. Roger Stanton.
<SYNC Start=1080637><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1081920><P Class=ENCC>Countermand the evacuation.
<SYNC Start=1084115><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1084200><P Class=ENCC>All forces already moving are to<br>return to their bases immediately.
<SYNC Start=1087954><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1088040><P Class=ENCC>Yes, sir.
<SYNC Start=1090031><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1091000><P Class=ENCC>Roger. My office, please.
<SYNC Start=1093434><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1093520><P Class=ENCC>Janet? Hi, this is Lynne. I'm gonna need<br>contacts for the following bases:
<SYNC Start=1098150><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1098240><P Class=ENCC>Point Mugu, Camp Pendleton.
<SYNC Start=1100390><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1105080><P Class=ENCC>I got word that military resources<br>were being moved out of LA.
<SYNC Start=1108629><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1108720><P Class=ENCC>- Yes.<br>- On your order.
<SYNC Start=1110597><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1110680><P Class=ENCC>Yes. I was implementing the plan.<br>I assumed you authorised it.
<SYNC Start=1116550><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1116640><P Class=ENCC>No, I told Rayburn not to<br>trigger any evacuation.
<SYNC Start=1120633><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1125640><P Class=ENCC>I should have double-checked everything<br>Rayburn told me before I took any action.
<SYNC Start=1129997><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1130080><P Class=ENCC>Mr President, it's inexcusable.<br>I take full responsibility.
<SYNC Start=1134392><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1134480><P Class=ENCC>We'll worry about that later.
<SYNC Start=1136948><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1137040><P Class=ENCC>I just told Lynne to countermand<br>the evacuation order.
<SYNC Start=1141875><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1141960><P Class=ENCC>- Make sure it happens immediately.<br>- Right away, sir.
<SYNC Start=1146431><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1152200><P Class=ENCC>- (secretary) Can I help you, Mr President?<br>- Yes. Tell Sherry I'll meet her in 20 minutes.
<SYNC Start=1157911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1158240><P Class=ENCC>You know how much<br>Daddy loves you, don't you?
<SYNC Start=1160993><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1163480><P Class=ENCC>And you know how sorry I am that<br>my little angel ever got hurt, right?
<SYNC Start=1168713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1176560><P Class=ENCC>Listen, pal, we're leaving now, OK?
<SYNC Start=1179711><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1180960><P Class=ENCC>So if anybody tries to talk to you,<br>you just... you don't say a word. OK?
<SYNC Start=1185954><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1186040><P Class=ENCC>Just pretend you're asleep.<br>You can do that, right?
<SYNC Start=1189999><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1190080><P Class=ENCC>- OK.<br>- OK.
<SYNC Start=1191399><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1191480><P Class=ENCC>- (door opens)<br>- Mr Matheson?
<SYNC Start=1193391><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1195120><P Class=ENCC>There's a call for you.
<SYNC Start=1197588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1197680><P Class=ENCC>A call?
<SYNC Start=1199398><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1201520><P Class=ENCC>- You can take it at the nurse's station.<br>- Why can't I take it in here?
<SYNC Start=1205513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1205600><P Class=ENCC>Because we don't have phones<br>in the rooms unless you order one.
<SYNC Start=1209752><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1214440><P Class=ENCC>You stay there, OK?
<SYNC Start=1217193><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1218840><P Class=ENCC>Megan, don't move.
<SYNC Start=1221149><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1225800><P Class=ENCC>- Looks like she'll be fine.<br>- OK.
<SYNC Start=1227756><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1227840><P Class=ENCC>- OK? Just running a few other tests.<br>- Is it gonna be much longer?
<SYNC Start=1231719><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1231800><P Class=ENCC>The phone's right in there.
<SYNC Start=1233518><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1233600><P Class=ENCC>So let's go take a look, OK?
<SYNC Start=1235989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1239800><P Class=ENCC>- This is Gary Matheson.<br>- (Miguel) Mr Matheson?
<SYNC Start=1242872><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1242960><P Class=ENCC>- Yeah, who is this?<br>- This is Trey in Accounts Receivable.
<SYNC Start=1246396><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1246480><P Class=ENCC>Our computers crashed, and we lost<br>a lot of your billing information.
<SYNC Start=1250871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1250960><P Class=ENCC>So if we could just go over it again...
<SYNC Start=1254032><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1254120><P Class=ENCC>- Can we do this another time, please?<br>- No, we need it now, sir.
<SYNC Start=1258113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1258200><P Class=ENCC>I can send someone up<br>to your daughter's room.
<SYNC Start=1260714><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1263160><P Class=ENCC>No. What do you need?
<SYNC Start=1265276><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1269720><P Class=ENCC>- Hi, Kim.<br>- Hi, sweetie.
<SYNC Start=1272234><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1276040><P Class=ENCC>- Listen, do you trust me?<br>- Yes.
<SYNC Start=1279874><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1280400><P Class=ENCC>I need to get you outta here.
<SYNC Start=1282709><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1282800><P Class=ENCC>All I can tell you is I'm doing this because<br>I love you and I want you to be safe. OK?
<SYNC Start=1288796><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1297000><P Class=ENCC>OK.
<SYNC Start=1298797><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1298880><P Class=ENCC>Come on.
<SYNC Start=1300552><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1300640><P Class=ENCC>- The expiration date?<br>- It expires March 2007, OK?
<SYNC Start=1304679><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1304760><P Class=ENCC>Great. Now if we could just<br>go over your billing address.
<SYNC Start=1308548><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1308640><P Class=ENCC>You know what? I'll come down later.
<SYNC Start=1311108><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1311200><P Class=ENCC>Mr Matheson?
<SYNC Start=1313191><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1325640><P Class=ENCC>Megan?
<SYNC Start=1327392><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1332800><P Class=ENCC>- My daughter's gone.<br>- Did you try the bathroom?
<SYNC Start=1335837><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1335920><P Class=ENCC>- Yes. She's not there.<br>- She might have been taken to radiology.
<SYNC Start=1339879><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1339960><P Class=ENCC>Well, find out where she is.
<SYNC Start=1342349><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1342440><P Class=ENCC>Yes, of course.
<SYNC Start=1344431><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1348600><P Class=ENCC>(woman over PA)<br>Dr Shapiro, 2262. Dr Shapiro, 2262.
<SYNC Start=1353196><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1372200><P Class=ENCC>- Where are we going, Kim?<br>- I told you, you have to trust me.
<SYNC Start=1376796><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1376880><P Class=ENCC>I just got off the phone. Come on.
<SYNC Start=1379440><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1379520><P Class=ENCC>I changed my mind. I don't wanna go.
<SYNC Start=1381715><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1381800><P Class=ENCC>My daddy's gonna get really mad, and then<br>he's gonna hurt me. I don't wanna go.
<SYNC Start=1386954><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1387040><P Class=ENCC>We need to go because<br>your dad is hurting you.
<SYNC Start=1389759><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1389840><P Class=ENCC>And your mom is trying to<br>stop him, but she can't.
<SYNC Start=1392638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1392720><P Class=ENCC>He's gonna keep hurting you<br>unless you leave with us.
<SYNC Start=1396235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1396320><P Class=ENCC>That's the only way anyone is gonna<br>stop him. Do you understand me?
<SYNC Start=1400199><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1400280><P Class=ENCC>Your daughter's not with<br>any of the departments.
<SYNC Start=1402794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1402880><P Class=ENCC>- Then where is she?<br>- I'm trying to figure that out.
<SYNC Start=1406031><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1406120><P Class=ENCC>- Did you see anyone near her room?<br>- No! Call security! Find me my daughter!
<SYNC Start=1410750><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1410840><P Class=ENCC>Megan, I need you to<br>breathe and calm down
<SYNC Start=1414515><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1414600><P Class=ENCC>and stop crying, so we can leave now. OK?
<SYNC Start=1417797><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1418800><P Class=ENCC>Come on.
<SYNC Start=1419994><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1420080><P Class=ENCC>I miss my mom. I want my mom!
<SYNC Start=1422594><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1423120><P Class=ENCC>I know. Come on with me. I know.
<SYNC Start=1425998><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1432760><P Class=ENCC>(radio) Look out for a nine-year-old girl<br>with blonde hair, striped top and blue jeans.
<SYNC Start=1438756><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1438840><P Class=ENCC>I've got Third Street, west door covered.
<SYNC Start=1441513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1445080><P Class=ENCC>In there.
<SYNC Start=1447071><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1469920><P Class=ENCC>Just got a team on the ground in Visalia,<br>and more coming in from Fresno.
<SYNC Start=1474710><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1474800><P Class=ENCC>Division's loaned us some men,<br>so I'm sending Miller along with you.
<SYNC Start=1478713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1478800><P Class=ENCC>I can handle her myself.
<SYNC Start=1480518><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1480600><P Class=ENCC>That's not what I'm worried about.
<SYNC Start=1483160><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1484120><P Class=ENCC>Do you think I'd sentence millions to death<br>just for the satisfaction of killing her?
<SYNC Start=1489877><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1493440><P Class=ENCC>I'll do my job.
<SYNC Start=1495431><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1495520><P Class=ENCC>I'm just sending Miller along<br>to make sure of that.
<SYNC Start=1499115><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1516720><P Class=ENCC>(Mason coughing)
<SYNC Start=1519188><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1525680><P Class=ENCC>You should go be with your family.
<SYNC Start=1529195><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1529280><P Class=ENCC>You should get on a plane.
<SYNC Start=1532078><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1534520><P Class=ENCC>- I'll call you when we're in the air.<br>- Yeah. Good.
<SYNC Start=1537592><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1542960><P Class=ENCC>David...
<SYNC Start=1543756><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1543840><P Class=ENCC>How did you find out about<br>the military evacuation?
<SYNC Start=1547037><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1547120><P Class=ENCC>I made some phone calls.
<SYNC Start=1548712><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1548800><P Class=ENCC>Just following up on a rumour.<br>I can't tell you any more than that.
<SYNC Start=1552509><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1552600><P Class=ENCC>You will tell me more,<br>and I will not ask you again.
<SYNC Start=1556593><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1558600><P Class=ENCC>I am not a member of your staff, David.<br>I am your wife.
<SYNC Start=1562115><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1562200><P Class=ENCC>Ex-wife, and you will tell me because<br>the safety and security of this country
<SYNC Start=1566273><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1566360><P Class=ENCC>is more important than your power plays.
<SYNC Start=1568874><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1568960><P Class=ENCC>You know, despite everything<br>that's happened, I love you.
<SYNC Start=1573078><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1573160><P Class=ENCC>- Oh, please.<br>- No, I always will.
<SYNC Start=1575549><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1575640><P Class=ENCC>Whether you believe it or not, everything that<br>I have done has been in your best interest.
<SYNC Start=1581715><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1583720><P Class=ENCC>If you won't give me<br>a second chance at your heart,
<SYNC Start=1586871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1586960><P Class=ENCC>let me help in the ways you know I can.
<SYNC Start=1589918><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1590000><P Class=ENCC>And I can't help you, David, unless you<br>give me some idea of what you're facing.
<SYNC Start=1595996><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1598480><P Class=ENCC>I was able to find something<br>your own staff couldn't find.
<SYNC Start=1601870><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1601960><P Class=ENCC>I didn't have to warn you.<br>I came here on my own accord.
<SYNC Start=1606750><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1612000><P Class=ENCC>Terrorists have planned<br>a strike against Los Angeles.
<SYNC Start=1615675><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1615760><P Class=ENCC>NSA thinks it'll be today.
<SYNC Start=1617910><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1618000><P Class=ENCC>What kind of strike?
<SYNC Start=1620468><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1620560><P Class=ENCC>Nuclear.
<SYNC Start=1622551><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1622640><P Class=ENCC>Oh, my G...
<SYNC Start=1624870><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1624960><P Class=ENCC>Oh, my God.
<SYNC Start=1626951><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1629840><P Class=ENCC>Talk to me, Sherry.
<SYNC Start=1632115><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1634400><P Class=ENCC>Come on.
<SYNC Start=1636152><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1636240><P Class=ENCC>I got the information about<br>the military evacuation
<SYNC Start=1639550><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1639640><P Class=ENCC>from someone inside<br>the defence department.
<SYNC Start=1642598><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1642680><P Class=ENCC>Who?
<SYNC Start=1644033><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1644120><P Class=ENCC>A high-level staffer. He's in the loop.<br>He owed me a favour.
<SYNC Start=1648830><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1648920><P Class=ENCC>But there's something more important.
<SYNC Start=1651388><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1651480><P Class=ENCC>He also told me that there are members of<br>your own administration allying against you.
<SYNC Start=1656315><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1656400><P Class=ENCC>They want control of your presidency.
<SYNC Start=1659995><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1660080><P Class=ENCC>That's why I came here today.
<SYNC Start=1662640><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1663880><P Class=ENCC>Who, Sherry?
<SYNC Start=1665393><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1665480><P Class=ENCC>People who disagree with your policies,<br>who want to impose their will on the country.
<SYNC Start=1670429><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1670520><P Class=ENCC>There have been deals made under<br>the table, David. Back-room promises.
<SYNC Start=1674911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1675000><P Class=ENCC>Now, I can keep digging, find out.
<SYNC Start=1678276><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1679800><P Class=ENCC>If you want my help.
<SYNC Start=1682268><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1698520><P Class=ENCC>If I accept your help, it won't be about us.
<SYNC Start=1701478><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1701560><P Class=ENCC>It'll be about doing<br>what's best for the country.
<SYNC Start=1705155><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1705240><P Class=ENCC>Sweetheart, you can call it<br>anything you want.
<SYNC Start=1709028><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1711400><P Class=ENCC>I'll get you a secure line<br>and a private place to make your calls.
<SYNC Start=1715154><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1715240><P Class=ENCC>Then I'll come to you<br>as soon as I find out more.
<SYNC Start=1719028><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1724600><P Class=ENCC>This had better not be<br>one of your manipulations.
<SYNC Start=1727956><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1728040><P Class=ENCC>The stakes are too high.
<SYNC Start=1730235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1751720><P Class=ENCC>- Dad?<br>- Hm?
<SYNC Start=1754393><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1754480><P Class=ENCC>- Reza's parents are here.<br>- I'm on the phone to your grandmother.
<SYNC Start=1757711><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1757800><P Class=ENCC>- I'll be right there.<br>- (door bell)
<SYNC Start=1760792><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1763640><P Class=ENCC>Oh!
<SYNC Start=1765437><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1765520><P Class=ENCC>You're here!
<SYNC Start=1767511><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1768320><P Class=ENCC>Welcome.
<SYNC Start=1769469><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1770160><P Class=ENCC>- So nice to see you, Kate.<br>- Come on in.
<SYNC Start=1772594><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1772680><P Class=ENCC>Thank you. The house looks beautiful.
<SYNC Start=1776150><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1776240><P Class=ENCC>Oh, thank you.
<SYNC Start=1778674><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1778760><P Class=ENCC>Well... you must be tired.<br>Let's go into the living room.
<SYNC Start=1783151><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1783240><P Class=ENCC>OK.
<SYNC Start=1784878><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1786440><P Class=ENCC>So, how is everyone holding up?
<SYNC Start=1789000><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1789080><P Class=ENCC>Not too bad.
<SYNC Start=1791071><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1791160><P Class=ENCC>Where is Reza?
<SYNC Start=1793435><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1793520><P Class=ENCC>Um, well, there's a small problem<br>we're dealing with.
<SYNC Start=1796751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1796840><P Class=ENCC>What kind of problem?
<SYNC Start=1798990><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1800400><P Class=ENCC>Um, some men from the government<br>are here talking to him.
<SYNC Start=1805190><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1806160><P Class=ENCC>About?
<SYNC Start=1808151><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1809360><P Class=ENCC>- It's a criminal investigation.<br>- I don't understand.
<SYNC Start=1813319><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1813400><P Class=ENCC>- It's very complicated.<br>- Kate, what is going on?
<SYNC Start=1816756><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1816840><P Class=ENCC>- It would be best if Reza told you himself.<br>- Told us what?
<SYNC Start=1821516><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1823560><P Class=ENCC>They're talking to Reza about his possible<br>involvement in terrorist activities.
<SYNC Start=1829749><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1829840><P Class=ENCC>- That is absurd!<br>- This must be a mistake.
<SYNC Start=1833071><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1833160><P Class=ENCC>- That's what they're trying to find out.<br>- You see?
<SYNC Start=1836232><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1836320><P Class=ENCC>Your country, you talk about tolerance,<br>you talk about freedom,
<SYNC Start=1840791><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1840880><P Class=ENCC>but you treat every Middle Easterner<br>like terrorist!
<SYNC Start=1844077><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1844160><P Class=ENCC>No! No, of course not.<br>I'm sure it'll all get sorted out.
<SYNC Start=1848392><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1848480><P Class=ENCC>- Rima, Hassan...<br>- Bob, do you know about this?
<SYNC Start=1851950><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1852040><P Class=ENCC>They just showed up about an hour ago.<br>I know nothing else. I'm sorry.
<SYNC Start=1857717><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1858920><P Class=ENCC>Don't worry. I'm sure it's nothing.
<SYNC Start=1861275><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1872200><P Class=ENCC>Wait for me in the parking lot.
<SYNC Start=1874350><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1874440><P Class=ENCC>If it's more than ten minutes, it means<br>they caught me, so take off without me.
<SYNC Start=1880197><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1881560><P Class=ENCC>You can't let them.<br>We are gonna leave all together.
<SYNC Start=1885109><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1887200><P Class=ENCC>OK?
<SYNC Start=1888519><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1893480><P Class=ENCC>Miguel.
<SYNC Start=1895152><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1896680><P Class=ENCC>Thank you.
<SYNC Start=1898671><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1915280><P Class=ENCC>Are you OK to walk by yourself?
<SYNC Start=1917794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1917880><P Class=ENCC>Yeah? Good girl.
<SYNC Start=1919711><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1923360><P Class=ENCC>Hey! Hey!
<SYNC Start=1925078><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1925160><P Class=ENCC>I got a male Hispanic, early 20s,<br>running out with a computer monitor.
<SYNC Start=1929153><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1929240><P Class=ENCC>Hey, come on!
<SYNC Start=1931231><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1936280><P Class=ENCC>Shh.
<SYNC Start=1937713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=1948360><P Class=ENCC>Go that way!
<SYNC Start=1949509><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2005120><P Class=ENCC>So, Ed, how are ya?
<SYNC Start=2007076><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2007160><P Class=ENCC>Don't bother, Nina.
<SYNC Start=2009116><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2009200><P Class=ENCC>I'm here because I have to be,<br>not because I'm your friend.
<SYNC Start=2014115><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2014200><P Class=ENCC>You're here because they think, after I help<br>stop the bomb, Jack will try to kill me.
<SYNC Start=2019479><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2019560><P Class=ENCC>Which, of course, he will.
<SYNC Start=2021710><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2022640><P Class=ENCC>And what if you can't stop him?
<SYNC Start=2025200><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2025280><P Class=ENCC>I mean, no offence,
<SYNC Start=2027316><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2027400><P Class=ENCC>but, Ed, let's face it, you're no match for Jack.
<SYNC Start=2031154><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2032480><P Class=ENCC>You're just not that ruthless.
<SYNC Start=2034710><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2038000><P Class=ENCC>So he manages to get around you<br>and pull the trigger. What happens then?
<SYNC Start=2043199><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2044880><P Class=ENCC>Because of the pardon, he knows if he<br>kills me, he'll spend the rest of his life in jail.
<SYNC Start=2049271><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2049360><P Class=ENCC>Jack, if you have some way to<br>shut her up I'm not thinking of...
<SYNC Start=2053239><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2053320><P Class=ENCC>Of course, Jack's mind is thinking<br>"That's not such a bad deal."
<SYNC Start=2058633><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2061480><P Class=ENCC>Small price to pay to avenge his wife's death.
<SYNC Start=2065439><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2065520><P Class=ENCC>But what about his daughter?<br>Is he thinking about her?
<SYNC Start=2069911><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2070880><P Class=ENCC>She's already lost one parent.<br>If he kills me, she'll have no one.
<SYNC Start=2075795><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2079800><P Class=ENCC>Jack knows I'm right.
<SYNC Start=2082439><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2082520><P Class=ENCC>He should just use me to stop the bomb,<br>and then go home to Kim.
<SYNC Start=2087435><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2090680><P Class=ENCC>She needs you, Jack.
<SYNC Start=2093558><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2113160><P Class=ENCC>- I didn't transfer that money.<br>- You transferred it into that account.
<SYNC Start=2117836><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2117920><P Class=ENCC>I didn't!
<SYNC Start=2119114><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2119200><P Class=ENCC>Then you better tell me who did,<br>or I'm taking you in!
<SYNC Start=2122397><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2122480><P Class=ENCC>Why are you doing this?
<SYNC Start=2124436><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2124520><P Class=ENCC>Friends of mine...
<SYNC Start=2126556><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2128160><P Class=ENCC>who were doing their best to protect<br>the citizens of this country
<SYNC Start=2132233><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2132320><P Class=ENCC>were murdered today... probably by<br>the same people you're funding!
<SYNC Start=2137917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2139520><P Class=ENCC>That a good enough reason for you?
<SYNC Start=2142671><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2142760><P Class=ENCC>I told you before...
<SYNC Start=2144751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2147440><P Class=ENCC>I don't know anything else.
<SYNC Start=2150238><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2168320><P Class=ENCC>Your parents.
<SYNC Start=2170311><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2177360><P Class=ENCC>All right, stand up, Reza.
<SYNC Start=2179635><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2183560><P Class=ENCC>Place your hands behind your head.
<SYNC Start=2186279><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2191520><P Class=ENCC>It's a shame. It's gonna break their heart.
<SYNC Start=2194910><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2196040><P Class=ENCC>I have to walk you right past them.
<SYNC Start=2198508><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2198600><P Class=ENCC>And they're gonna see who their son really is.
<SYNC Start=2202388><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2205520><P Class=ENCC>Wait!
<SYNC Start=2207158><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2211520><P Class=ENCC>I confirmed the transfers,<br>but I didn't make them.
<SYNC Start=2215798><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2215880><P Class=ENCC>I was just covering the records.
<SYNC Start=2219031><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2220160><P Class=ENCC>I didn't want him to get into trouble.
<SYNC Start=2223232><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2224680><P Class=ENCC>Who? Who are you covering for?
<SYNC Start=2228309><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2230840><P Class=ENCC>Come on, who transferred that money<br>into Syed Ali's accounts?
<SYNC Start=2235914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2242400><P Class=ENCC>Bob Warner.
<SYNC Start=2244391><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2246880><P Class=ENCC>Marie's father.
<SYNC Start=2248871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2265480><P Class=ENCC>- (Megan groans)<br>- What?
<SYNC Start=2267072><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2267160><P Class=ENCC>- What's the matter?<br>- I don't feel very well.
<SYNC Start=2269879><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2282960><P Class=ENCC>Come on, Miguel.
<SYNC Start=2284791><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2286480><P Class=ENCC>- (screams)<br>- Get away from us!
<SYNC Start=2288471><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2288560><P Class=ENCC>Give her to me, or I will make sure<br>you go to prison for 20 years.
<SYNC Start=2291916><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2292000><P Class=ENCC>- I know how she got hurt.<br>- That was an accident!
<SYNC Start=2294833><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2294920><P Class=ENCC>Like Carla's bruises?
<SYNC Start=2296512><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2296600><P Class=ENCC>(Megan screams)
<SYNC Start=2298591><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2316440><P Class=ENCC>- It's OK.<br>- Miguel...
<SYNC Start=2318510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2324680><P Class=ENCC>(Miguel) Let's just get outta here.
<SYNC Start=2327433><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2330520><P Class=ENCC>Get his car keys.
<SYNC Start=2332795><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2340400><P Class=ENCC>(speaking Arabic)
<SYNC Start=2342516><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2355240><P Class=ENCC>- Reza.<br>- Sweetheart, angel.
<SYNC Start=2358073><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2360880><P Class=ENCC>- You OK?<br>- Yes.
<SYNC Start=2362598><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2363920><P Class=ENCC>- They know I didn't do anything.<br>- Oh, thank God.
<SYNC Start=2367674><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2367760><P Class=ENCC>- We can get married today.<br>- I don't know, sweetheart.
<SYNC Start=2372390><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2373480><P Class=ENCC>Mr Warner.
<SYNC Start=2375232><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2376520><P Class=ENCC>Could you follow me, please, sir?
<SYNC Start=2378715><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2378800><P Class=ENCC>- What does this have to do with me?<br>- Just come with me, please.
<SYNC Start=2383271><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2386320><P Class=ENCC>What did you tell them?
<SYNC Start=2388595><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2388680><P Class=ENCC>The truth.
<SYNC Start=2390830><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2390920><P Class=ENCC>- The truth? What do you mean, the truth?<br>- Please, my parents are very upset.
<SYNC Start=2395994><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2409200><P Class=ENCC>(Kim) Hurry.
<SYNC Start=2410838><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2426400><P Class=ENCC>Yeah.
<SYNC Start=2427958><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2428280><P Class=ENCC>Yeah. OK.
<SYNC Start=2430271><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2431200><P Class=ENCC>The team's in Visalia.<br>We'll have tactical and field units.
<SYNC Start=2434875><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2434960><P Class=ENCC>We have confirmation that they're in place?
<SYNC Start=2437838><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2437920><P Class=ENCC>Probably in the air.
<SYNC Start=2440070><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2442720><P Class=ENCC>We'll have air traffic, um...
<SYNC Start=2445518><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2448160><P Class=ENCC>Air traffic priority?
<SYNC Start=2450116><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2450960><P Class=ENCC>Yeah...
<SYNC Start=2452996><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2453080><P Class=ENCC>Tra...
<SYNC Start=2455275><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2455360><P Class=ENCC>Jack...
<SYNC Start=2456156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
<SYNC Start=2456240><P Class=ENCC>It's all right, Ed. It's all right. Just take it easy.
<SYNC Start=2459516><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp
